OL,5, A university student says he felt      
OL,6, forced to break the law to earn enough 
OL,7, money to afford his degree.            
OL,9,FWorking multiple jobs alongside his    
OL,10,Fcourse at Swansea University, Tyler    
OL,11,Frealised he couldn't get the degree he 
OL,12,Fwanted unless something changed.       
OL,14,FWith no family support, the 24-year-old
OL,15,Fsays he thinks more support should be  
OL,16,Fgiven to those from poorer backgrounds 
OL,17,Fwanting to go to university.           
OL,19,FA Swansea University spokesperson said 
OL,20,Fstudents have access to financial aid. 
